  "title": "Software Engineer (Contract)",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>You will be carrying out design and development of large scale mission critical applications using latest java technologies<br /></p><ul><li>Carrying out design, development according to functional specifications</li><li>Performing development using Java, Microservices and RDBMS</li><li>Assist in carrying out SIT and UAT</li><li>Assisting in ci/cd for continuous development and deployment</li><li>Ensure compliance with coding, performance, and security standards.</li><li>Collaborate closely with stakeholders, manage timelines, and provide clear status updates.</li><li></li></ul><h2>Technical Skills</h2><ul><li>Min 8 years of experience in java application development</li><li>Experience in banking industry is a plus</li><li>Strong expertise in Java, J2EE, Microservices, API development, REST webservices</li><li>Strong experience in OO development</li><li>Experience working with middleware</li><li>SQL, relational database concepts, query optimization</li></ul><p><br />Interested candidates please email your latest resume to subagio@tangspac.com</p>",
